import jax
import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1):
    v0 = jnp.subtract(x0, x1)
    v1 = jnp.minimum(x0, x1)
    v2 = jnp.minimum(v0, v1)
    v3 = jnp.multiply(x1, x1)
    v4 = jnp.cos(v1)
    v5 = jnp.subtract(v4, v1)
    v6 = jnp.minimum(v2, x1)
    v7 = jnp.subtract(v3, v2)
    v8 = jnp.maximum(v0, v6)
    return v8
